comment5.text=\r\n\ Act\ -\ Start\ by\ checking\ health,\ then\ determine\ if\ it\ is\ time\ to\ act\ yet.\ \ If\ so,\ \r\n\ call\ checkInput\ to\ act\ according\ to\ keyboard\ input.\r\n
