comment6.target=void\ checkHealth()
comment6.text=\r\n\ Checks\ health\ of\ player\ and\ changes\ images\ if\ damaged\ and\ checks\ for\ death.\r\n\ If\ wounded,\ change\ image\ set\ to\ wounded\ sprites.\r\n\ If\ dead,\ call\ the\ gameOver\ method.\r\n
